<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1 class="card-heading">About Me</h1>
    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "chris.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-image' %>
        <p>Chris, Jessica and Luke</p>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h5><%= skill.title %></h5>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8 text-left">
        <p>As a software developer who focuses on creating functional web applications, most of my clients are deligted with the end result. While others have the ability to create beautiful or "stunning" websites, I find most of them are far too complex and not friendly to the people who are interacting with them.</p>

        <p>I believe Jason Fried said it best:</p>

        <blockquote class="blockquote text-center font-italic">"Simple" is a tricky word, it can mean a lot of things. To us, it just means clear. That doesn't always mean total reduction, or minimalism - somtimes, to make things clearer, you have to add a step.</blockquote>

        <p>My clients and I travel a different road together. We choose to focus on creating web apps that are easy to use, well designed and functional. Most importantly, they are simple.</p>

        <p>
          <button 
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button 
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-body card-block">
              <h5 class="card-title">Wicked Reports</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Head of Customer Service & Data Analysis - 2016-2018.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card card-body card-block">
              <h5 class="card-title">Marine Essentials</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Project Manager - 2015-2016.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card card-body card-block">
              <h5 class="card-title">Smartbox Web Marketing</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Client CRM Manager - 2014-2015.</p>
            </div>             
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-body card-block">
              <h5 class="card-title">University of N. Colorado</h5>
              <p class="card-text">B.A. Education - 2009.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>